{"tid":1309802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[長期頂置][必入]打機心得","createTime":"2019-07-12T11:10:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T11:51:23.000Z","uid":143499,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8d8d7fe8dd85be4641effa1e4697ac306b602b19","tid":1309802,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:10:47.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n小弟打機發現唔少網友打怪期間喺前線食煙<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我知口癮好難戎，亦衷心多謝大家聯機<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過請咁多位大佬可唔可行遠少少食，盡量唔好喺frontline或密集位食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟淪陷日朝早守龍and道防線 ; 由於情報錯誤， 好多人以為夏X道朝頭早放咗催淚彈， 所以龍and道多好人都上咗豬嘴戒備<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n問題就嚟喇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我個6006啱啱開包裝，四個鐘頭全程有人喺隔離食煙，ai都未放催淚彈，濾芯已經接近報廢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能食煙有焦油嘅關係，所以類咀消耗得特別快<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到ai真係放催淚彈，濾芯已經消耗得七七八八<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我知咁多位隊友坐埋同一條船<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不知道唔食煙係會好辛苦<br />\n<br />\n但係麻煩可唔可以行遠少少食<br />\n<br />\n咁落去未打仗消耗品已經消耗得好快<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再加上有啲網友防毒裝備都冇，長時間企喺你隔離食二手煙真係好辛苦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係又唔好意思講出口，驚得罪大家<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為好難得今次大和解，大家都action<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以小弟真係求下大家食煙麻煩行遠少少<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n        <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc5847f0a024ed5f23dba01ec242525aba331573","tid":1309802,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:11:18.000Z","msg":"麻煩咁多位大佬幫手推下"},{"pid":"cd17e164db53c73e4afc94d00859cea1114fac48","tid":1309802,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:14:42.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6de7b2e1dd467de925d1d267f3d3e33ae311032c","tid":1309802,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:16:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87240a0c68298f33721da27ad5c233189f980339","tid":1309802,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:17:08.000Z","msg":"幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc5c29c33e7dd18cfda010761ca4bb37165a002a","tid":1309802,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:18:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24748dccc40b21cc27053eed3c845cd6b8985735","tid":1309802,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:19:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"540de846385a4f405cd83401fced597ed41e0de7","tid":1309802,"uid":208017,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:22:13.000Z","msg":"冇人想知"},{"pid":"cb93557202a83128b4c97202fd05ddecab59d481","tid":1309802,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"540de846385a4f405cd83401fced597ed41e0de7","tid":1309802,"uid":208017,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:22:13.000Z","msg":"冇人想知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T11:22:42.000Z","msg":"長期食二手煙真係好辛苦㗎大佬"},{"pid":"7609ba